			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Go to\r\nlarian://bookmark?mod=GustavDev&level=BGO_Main_A&camPos=3.229594;52.549690;10.047598&camTarget=3.228639;52.118618;10.949918\r\n\r\nKill all FFs with Ctrl+Shift+K. Click on the SW to talk.\r\nAlternatively, give your character some gold and BALDURIAN tag. Walk through checkpoint by paying gold and saying that you're Baldurian. Then after access allowed, talk to Steel Watcher."
				},
